    "attributes": {
        "action": "Allow all children to take 10 days holiday leave during term time.",
        "additional_details": "This will give families the opportunity to take their children on holiday outside of peak times, which are often the most expensive times to travel.\r\n\r\nThis would be of particular benefit to less privileged children whose parents cannot afford peak season prices or the fines associated with taking children out of school during term time.\r\n\r\nTravelling and experiencing different cultures is important for all to experience and offers learning that isn\u2019t available in the classroom.",
        "background": "Allow all children and young people to take 10 days holiday leave during term time, without the risk of being fined.",
